{"tid":1354172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：為何要與穿白衣的人割席？","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T05:53:47.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2de60556768ec6df887b2a34218497d995b7b0","tid":1354172,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"元朗周日晚發生白衣人襲擊市民事件，當日曾被拍得與一群白衣人握手的新界西立法會議員何君堯，在出席港台節目錄影後被問及，會否與白衣人割席時，反問為何要與穿白衣的人割席，與他們握手並不代表贊同任何犯法行為。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，市民無論身穿甚麼顏色衣服，都不應訴諸暴力，強調任何人士犯法都要受到法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，他在新界並非很有影響力，但都會呼籲所有人，包括新界村民要冷靜，又建議民主派不要煽動市民訴諸暴力。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯離開港台廣播大廈時，一班市民在門口守候，有人向他掟鞋及指罵，何君堯呼籲冷靜，又邀請大家下月4日出席集會傾談。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2198132/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2198132%2F&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=2f773c8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2198132/</a>"},{"pid":"4007e3aa5681d2bbaa91a0da863a4ff9a4c2a16f","tid":1354172,"uid":61968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"386b6765a51f5bbf92050dc0c04586face6de147","tid":1354172,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:51:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他稱，他在新界並非很有影響力，但都會呼籲所有人，包括新界村民要冷靜，又建議民主派不要煽動市民訴諸暴力。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個算唔算割"},{"pid":"b659cbcdee5b6feb619c379ac43ead321b599ebb","tid":1354172,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"可惜以民建聯為首既親中派已經同你割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}